snippet.title: Clear Vision Elite Flash Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Clear Vision Elite is the 3rd game in the Clear Vision series.  Jake is down to his final list of target.  One by one, you cross of the list and help Jake get closer to his retirement.  

There's a good bit of weapons and upgrades to buy this time as well which was a nice addition.  This is one of my favorite flash games, but it has a lot of glitches that can soft lock the game such as reloading too quickly.
